Privacy policy
MBCC Foods (Ireland) Ltd is a controller of your personal data. We respect your data and your privacy is important to us.
This Privacy Notice explains what personal data we collect and how it is used.  This notice also explains what rights you have over your personal data and how you can use those rights.
You have the right to object to some of the processing which MBCC Foods (Ireland) Ltd carries out.  More information about your rights and how to exercise these is set out in the “
Your rights
” section of this notice.
MBCC Foods (Ireland) Ltd operates the Costa franchise in Ireland and Northern Ireland under license.  registered office is MBCC Foods (Ireland) Unit 12 Retail Park, Eastgate, Little Island, Cork TX45 KXO6.
