For any queries relating to data protection please contact
privacyofficer@mbccfoodsireland.com
or by writing to them at Privacy Officer, MBCC Foods (Ireland), Unit 12 Retail Park, Eastgate, Little Island, Cork TX45 KX06.
If we make any changes or updates to this notice we will communicate these.
11. Which Costa entity is the controller?
The controller for your information is MBCC Foods (Ireland) Ltd, Unit 12 Retail Park, Eastgate, Little Island, Cork TX45 KX06. MBCC Foods (Ireland) Ltd runs the Costa Coffee Club within Ireland and Northern Ireland.
We operate as a franchisee. Our stores are an independent business that operates across Ireland and Northern Ireland.